nws5_01l.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went up 10 percentage points

nws5_01p.description: The minimum of L10 or S10

nws5_01s.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went down 10 percentage points

nws5_02l.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went up 20 percentage points

nws5_02p.description: The minimum of L20 or S20

nws5_02s.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went down 20 percentage points

nws5_10_minutes.description: The percent change in price in the first 10 minutes following the news release

nws5_120_minutes.description: The percent change in price in the first 120 minutes following the news release

nws5_1l.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went up 1 percentage point

nws5_1p.description: The minimum of L1 or S1

nws5_1s.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went down 1 percentage point

nws5_2l.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went up 2 percentage points

nws5_2p.description: The minimum of L2 or S2

nws5_2s.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went down 2 percentage points

nws5_30_minutes.description: The percent change in price in the first 30 minutes following the news release

nws5_30_seconds.description: The percent change in price in the 30 seconds following the news release

nws5_3l.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went up 3 percentage points

nws5_3p.description: The minimum of L3 or S3

nws5_3s.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went down 3 percentage points

nws5_4l.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went up 4 percentage points

nws5_4p.description: The minimum of L4 or S4

nws5_4s.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went down 4 percentage points

nws5_57l.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went up 7.5 percentage points

nws5_57p.description: The minimum of L75 or S75

nws5_57s.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went down 7.5 percentage points

nws5_5_minutes.description: The percent change in price in the first 5 minutes following the news release

nws5_5l.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went up 5 percentage points

nws5_5p.description: The minimum of L5 or S5

nws5_5s.description: Number of minutes that elapsed before price went down 5 percentage points

nws5_60_minutes.description: The percent change in price in the first 60 minutes following the news release

nws5_90_minutes.description: The percent change in price in the first 90 minutes following the news release

nws5_allticks.description: Total number of ticks for the trading day

nws5_allvwap.description: Volume-weighted average price of all sessions

nws5_eodhigh.description: Highest price reached between the time of news and the end of the session

nws5_eodlow.description: Lowest price reached between the time of news and the end of the session

nws5_eodvwap.description: Volume-weighted average price of the session from the time of news until the end of the session

nws5_highexcstddev.description: (EODHigh - TONLast)/StdDev, where StdDev is one standard deviation for the close price for 30 calendar days

nws5_lowexcstddev.description: (TONLast - EODLow)/StdDev, where StdDev is one standard deviation for the close price for 30 calendar days

nws5_mainvwap.description: Main session volume weighted average price

nws5_maxdnamt.description: The price at the time of the news minus the after-the-news low

nws5_maxdown.description: Percent change from the price at the time of the news to the after-the-news low

nws5_maxup.description: Percent change from the price at the time of the news to the after-the-news high

nws5_maxupamt.description: The after-the-news high minus the price at the time of the news

nws5_minute.description: The percent change in price in the first minute following the news release

nws5_mktcap_1000.description: Reported market capitalization for the calendar day of the session

nws5_peratio.description: Reported price-to-earnings ratio for the calendar day of the session

nws5_prevday.description: Percent change between the previous day's open and close

nws5_range.description: (Session High Price - Session Low Price) / Session Low Price

nws5_rangeamt.description: Session High Price - Session Low Price

nws5_rangestddev.description: (RangeAmt-AvgRange)/RangeStdDev, where AvgRange is the average of the daily range, and RangeStdDev is one standard deviation for the daily range, both for 30 calendar days

nws5_result.description: Percent change between the price at the time of the news release to the price at the close of the session

nws5_shortinterest.description: Total number of shares sold short divided by total number of shares outstanding

nws5_sl.description: Whether a long or short position would have been more advantageous: If (EODHigh - Last) > (Last - EODLow) Then LS = 1; If (EODHigh - Last) = (Last - EODLow) Then LS= 0; If (EODHigh - Last) < (Last - EODLow) Then LS = -1.

nws5_spyclose.description: Price of SPY at close of session

nws5_spylast.description: Last Price of the SPY at the time of the news

nws5_tonhigh.description: Highest price reached during the session before the time of news

nws5_tonlast.description: Price at the time of news

nws5_tonlow.description: Lowest price reached during the session before the time of the news

nws5_volumestddev.description: (CurrentVolume - AvgVol) / VolStDev, where AvgVol is the average of the daily volume, and VolStDev is one standard deviation for the daily volume, both for 30 calendar days
